README
------

Steps to use NextRoute to power your own app's twitter account:

1) Create a twitter account for your application. For e.g: @nextroute

2) Set the 'READ & WRITE DIRECT MESSAGES' perm for your app.

3) Allow your application to access the newly created twitter account (e.g: @nextroute).

4) Edit the file nextroute.py and update it with your app's access tokens.

5) Run: python nextroute.py.
